    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are confirmed out-of-scope per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for Class II, medium-influence, MRL 2 profile. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD prediction of hemolysis index within 15% of experimental reference across the full COU operating envelope. The relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied at all 5 flow-speed combinations. The credibility body of evidence is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission for the CPB device tolerance analysis.",
